cooking time. We used X-Large eggs (59 g) in this recipe; using smaller eggs will reduce the cooking time. Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for timings for both soft and hard boiled eggs. Take care when peeling soft boiled eggs.","You can replace the ghee with oil of choice.","Serve with rice, if desired."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","4 portions"]}